OL,3,CWhy are we seeing more hail even
OL,4,Cthough the weather is warming up?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHow big can hail actually get?
OL,13,FThe largest hailstone ever officially
OL,14,Frecorded fell in Vivian, South Dakota,
OL,15,FUSA on July 23, 2010.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
