OL,3,CWhy are we seeing more hail even
OL,4,Cthough the weather is warming up?
OL,6,FHaving said that, the largest hail
OL,7,Fever recorded in the UK was around the
OL,8,Fsize of tennis ball, in September 1958
OL,9,Fin Horsham, West Sussex - and that's
OL,10,Fcertainly large enough to cause some
OL,11,Fdamage!
